=== Marginalized_Groups ===
Social media bans don't affect everyone equally. # diagram: marginalized_isolation.jpg

For some young people, online spaces provide something they can't find anywhere else:
• LGBTQ+ teenagers in conservative areas
• Autistic youth who share their communication style
• Disabled young people for whom physical meetups are difficult
• Kids in rural areas with few nearby peers
• Marginalized ethnic or religious backgrounds finding shared experiences

