=== Research_Details ===
Australian researchers found:
• Bans might mitigate some harm, but also restrict positive experiences
• Bans push young people to less-regulated spaces
• Bans create false security among parents
• Risks to social connection highest for disabled, autistic, LGBTQ+, and rural youth

